	<div class="article-section" id="1">
		<br><h1>Accounts</h1>

		<h2>- How do I open a personal/ business account?</h2>


		<p>Very simple, visit our website www.Kiyanpay.com and click on sign up. Please remember to have identification with you so that your account can be opened in less than 15 mins!</p>

		<h2>- What age do I need to be to apply for an account?</h2>

		<p>Currently you must be 18 or older to hold an account with Kiyanpay.</p>

		<h2>- Do I need to be a UK resident to apply for an account?</h2>

		<p>Yes, you currently need to be resident in the UK to hold an account with KiyanPay. We hope to expand in the near future.</p>

		<h2>- What documents can I use to open an account?</h2>

		<h2>Documents for a company :</h2>

		<p><li>Certificate of incorporation/registration;</li>
		   <li>Recent excerpt from a state company registry;</li>
           <li>Certificate of incumbency;</li>
           <li>Certificate of good standing;</li>
           <li>Memorandum/articles of incorporation/association/registration;</li>
           <li>Another similar document;</li></p>

        <h2>2. A document allowing to establish all the UBOs of the company, such as:</h2>

        <p><li>Shareholder registry;</li>
		   <li>Statement of information;</li>
           <li>Recent excerpt from a state company registry;</li>
           <li>Certificate of incumbency;</li>
           <li>Memorandum/articles of incorporation/association/registration;</li>
           <li>Trust agreement;</li>
           <li>Another similar document.</li></p>	

        <h2>Individuals:</h2>

        <p><li> UK/EEA/EU and Swiss passport</li>
		   <li>Valid full UK photocard Driving licence</li>
           <li>Valid full UK provisional photocard Driving licence</li>
           <li>Valid full EU member state national ID photocard</li>
           <li>Valid firearm certificate or shotgun licence</li>
           <li>Valid old style UK Driving Licence (no photo)</li>
           <li>Valid Passport/EU national ID Card in date</li>
           <li>HMRC documentation</li>
           <li>Valid passport* with current Visa (with at least six months left on it) or a Biometric Resident Permit (Both sides of Biometric Resident permit required).</li></p>	

        <h2>- How long does it take for the account to be opened?</h2>

        <p>The account will be opened on the same day. If we do require further information we will contact you within 24 hours of requesting the account to be opened.</p>

        <h2>- Do you need a selfie when signing up?</h2>

        <p>We will need a selfie for verification and for us to stay compliant with the regulations. This is for us to accept an account to be opened online as we are not able to see your face in person. We use selfie photo to check your face matches the photo ID. This will prevent identity fraud.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="article-section" id="2">
		<br><h1>Business Account</h1>

		<h2>- How do I verify my business?</h2>

		<p>There are a few easy steps to complete registration, let me tell you how!
		We would love to know more about yourself- - As you will be the primary account holder, we will need information to verify yourself such as DOB, address, country of residence etc.
		We love to know more about your business – we will ask for your business name, business sector and confirmation of directors and shareholders.
		Selfie time – you will be prompted to upload the documentation based on the information you have provided and take a photo.
		That’s it! – your account would be opened within 15 minutes. If we do require further information we will contact you with 24 hours of requesting the account opening.</p>

		<h2>- Why do I need to verify my business?</h2>

		<p>We want to make sure your money is safe with us and to do so verification is one of the ways and comply with the financial regulations. This helps us verify who you are and if your business is currently trading. The process is designed to be quick and easy for you.</p>
</div>
<div class="article-section" id="3">
